                <div id="article-container">
        
                    <h3><a href="">About C++</a></h3>

                    <div id="article-summary">

                        <p>C++ is general-purpose object-oriented programming (OOP) language developed by Bjarne Stroustrup.Originally, C++ was called “C with classes,”</p>
                        <p>as it had all the properties of the C language with the addition of user-defined data types called “classes.” It was renamed C++ in 1983.
                        <p>C++ is considered an intermediate-level language, as it includes both high and low-level language features.</p>

                    </div>
